Question: Are the pens next to the cat small and colorful?

Reference Answer: Yes, the pens are small and colorful.

Image path: ./sampled_GQA/n433692.jpg

Program:

```
BOX0=LOC(image=IMAGE,object='cat')
IMAGE0=CROP_LEFTOF(image=IMAGE,box=BOX0)
BOX1=LOC(image=IMAGE0,object='pens')
ANSWER0=COUNT(box=BOX1)
ANSWER1=EVAL(expr="'yes' if {ANSWER0} > 0 else 'no'")
BOX2=LOC(image=IMAGE,object='cat')
IMAGE1=CROP_RIGHTOF(image=IMAGE,box=BOX2)
BOX3=LOC(image=IMAGE1,object='pens')
ANSWER2=COUNT(box=BOX3)
ANSWER3=EVAL(expr="'yes' if {ANSWER2} > 0 else 'no'")
BOX4=LOC(image=IMAGE,object='cat')
IMAGE2=CROP_BELOW(image=IMAGE,box=BOX4)
BOX5=LOC(image=IMAGE2,object='pens')
ANSWER4=COUNT(box=BOX5)
ANSWER5=EVAL(expr="'yes' if {ANSWER4} > 0 else 'no'")
ANSWER6=EVAL(expr="'yes' if {ANSWER1} == 'yes' and {ANSWER3} == 'yes' and {ANSWER5} == 'yes' else 'no'")
FINAL_RESULT=RESULT(var=ANSWER6)
```
